ft-field activities.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Endless kilometres\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"the black line\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2830}, {\"ngram\": \"the bottom\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2844}, {\"ngram\": \"a pool\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2854}, {\"ngram\": \"rock climbing\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2885}, {\"ngram\": \"calisthenics\", \"from\": 2890, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"other left-field activities\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard to explain the two-year process that it took to get here and the route I took,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 3038, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the two-year process\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2981}, {\"ngram\": \"the route\", \"from\": 3011, \"to\": 3020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That act of creation, effectively, over the last two years ... being the guinea pig and seeing where it would take me, is something that I am going to be most proud of.\\\"\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That act\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"creation\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3061}, {\"ngram\": \"the last two years\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"the guinea pig\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McEvoy released teasers about his training before Paris.\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3262, \"end\": 3267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.99999999218835, \"rank\": 7.811425321251623e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McEvoy\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"teasers\", \"from\": 3228, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"his training